        {"number": 2, "title_zh": "领受圣餐的预备", "title_en": "Preparation for Receiving Communion", "summary_zh": "教导信徒如何在圣餐前预备自己的心。", "summary_en": "Teaches believers how to prepare their hearts before Communion.", "key_quotes": ["'不配地领受圣餐是危险的——但因害怕而不领受同样是损失。' / 'Receiving Communion unworthily is dangerous—but refusing it out of fear is equally a loss.'"]},
        {"number": 3, "title_zh": "在圣餐中遇见基督", "title_en": "Meeting Christ in the Supper", "summary_zh": "描述信徒如何在圣餐中以信心真实地遇见基督。", "summary_en": "Describes how believers truly encounter Christ by faith in the Supper.", "key_quotes": ["'在圣餐桌前，我们的灵魂以信心的嘴唇吃喝基督的身体和宝血。' / 'At the Communion table, our souls eat and drink Christ's body and blood with the lips of faith.'"]}
