        {"number": 2, "title_zh": "圣经中的经济原则", "title_en": "Biblical Economic Principles", "summary_zh": "从圣经中提取关于经济和商业的核心原则。", "summary_en": "Extracts core principles about economics and business from Scripture.", "key_quotes": ["'私有财产不是贪婪的产物——它是上帝赐给人类管理资源的方式。' / 'Private property is not a product of greed—it is God's means of giving humans stewardship of resources.'"]},
        {"number": 3, "title_zh": "慷慨与管家", "title_en": "Generosity and Stewardship", "summary_zh": "探讨财富管理和慷慨给予的圣经教导。", "summary_en": "Explores biblical teaching on wealth management and generous giving.", "key_quotes": ["'赚取财富和慷慨施与不是矛盾的——两者都是上帝所喜悦的。' / 'Earning wealth and giving generously are not contradictory—both are pleasing to God.'"]}
